description: Close a completed sprint for {{project.name}} with bidirectional outflow.
---

Run the project's `close-sprint` skill at `.github/skills/close-sprint/SKILL.md`, which is a thin overlay over the `praxis` plugin's `close-sprint` skill.

Both shores must be updated (wave + dashboard on the product side; ADRs + capability layout + handbook on the engineering side) before the sprint file at `{{paths.sprints}}/SPRINT.<ID>-<slug>.md` is deleted.
